  "task": "/home/user/Documents/wf_fix.drawio contains 5 series-connected shapes with white fill: 'Input' (cell id 2), 'Clean' (cell id 3), 'Transform' (cell id 4), 'Check' (cell id 5, a diamond/rhombus), 'Save' (cell id 6).\n\nApply these changes:\n1. fillColor 'Input' (id 2) → #dae8fc (blue)\n2. fillColor 'Clean' (id 3) → #d5e8d4 (green)\n3. fillColor 'Transform' (id 4) → #d5e8d4 (green)\n4. fillColor 'Check' (id 5) → #fff2cc (yellow)\n5. fillColor 'Save' (id 6) → #f8cecc (red)\n6. Add a new shape labeled 'Reject'.\n7. Draw an arrow from 'Check' to 'Reject' (the failure branch).\n\nThe page must end up with exactly 6 vertices total. Persist to /home/user/Documents/wf_fix.drawio.",
